<item>
            <title>[SENTRY-2032] Leading Slashes need to removed when creating HMS path entries</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SENTRY-2032</link>
                <project id="12314720" key="SENTRY">Sentry (Retired)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When retrieving full path image update, we split a path by &quot;/&quot; and create HMS Path entries. However, the leading &quot;/&quot; presence will cause issues because on splitting the value at index 0 will be empty. This will affect the creation of HMS path entries. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13116546">SENTRY-2032</key>
            <summary>Leading Slashes need to removed when creating HMS path entries</summary>
